Paper: hep-th/9404052

Date: 1994-04-08

Title: Quantum Algebras for Maximal Motion Groups of N-Dimensional Flat Spaces

Authors: A. Ballesteros, F.J. Herranz, M.A. del Olmo and M. Santander

Comments: 10 pages, AMS-TEX file

Journal-ref: Lett.Math.Phys. 33 (1995) 273-281

An embedding method to get $q$-deformations for the non--semisimple algebrasgenerating the motion groups of $N$--dimensional flat spaces is presented. Thismethod gives a global and simultaneous scheme of $q$-deformation for all$iso(p,q)$ algebras and for those ones obtained from them by someIn\"on\"u--Wigner contractions, such as the $N$--dimensional Euclidean,Poincar\'e and Galilei algebras.